<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>The community as a whole is more than welcome to talk about and propose general rules regarding rotations or server rules or whatever else, but rotation rules should always be determined by the guilds that are on a rotation.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->Apparently we can make 'general rules regarding rotations' and 'server rules' (dammit, ah tuld y'all ta stop shit'n in da durn woods!) ...but really, rotations are above our level of intelligence to comprehend y'all's big wurds?  We'z too stoopid ta knowe how ta surf dat der new fangled infoormatun hayway...<br>
